{
  "video_id": "DOisAG9yoNk",
  "title": "3 psychological tricks to help you save money | The Way We Work, a TED series",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 262300.0,
      "end_time": 265835.0,
      "text": "So now that I was 4,000 dollars in the hole, I did two things."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 265859.0,
      "end_time": 268412.0,
      "text": "The first is that I unlinked my credit card"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 268437.0,
      "end_time": 269902.0,
      "text": "from my car-sharing apps."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 269926.0,
      "end_time": 274220.0,
      "text": "Instead, I linked a debit card that only had 300 dollars a month."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 274460.0,
      "end_time": 275244.0,
      "text": "If I needed more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 275268.0,
      "end_time": 278118.0,
      "text": "I had to go through the whole process of adding a new card,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 278142.0,
      "end_time": 282594.0,
      "text": "and we know that every click, every barrier, changes our behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 165.0,
      "end_time": 1924.0,
      "text": "We all know that saving is important"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 1948.0,
      "end_time": 3942.0,
      "text": "and is something that we should be doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 3966.0,
      "end_time": 6323.0,
      "text": "And yet, overall, we&#39;re doing less and less of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 6347.0,
      "end_time": 8949.0,
      "text": "[The Way We Work]"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 10622.0,
      "end_time": 12209.0,
      "text": "We know what we need to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 12233.0,
      "end_time": 14368.0,
      "text": "The question is: How do we do it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 14392.0,
      "end_time": 16218.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s what I&#39;m here to teach you."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 16242.0,
      "end_time": 19750.0,
      "text": "Your savings behavior isn&#39;t a question of how smart you are"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 19990.0,
      "end_time": 20609.0,
      "text": "or how much willpower you have."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 20633.0,
      "end_time": 23910.0,
      "text": "The amount we save depends on the environmental cues around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 23934.0,
      "end_time": 25347.0,
      "text": "Let me give you an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 25371.0,
      "end_time": 27878.0,
      "text": "We ran a study in which, in one group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 27903.0,
      "end_time": 30799.0,
      "text": "we showed people their income on a monthly basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 30823.0,
      "end_time": 34466.0,
      "text": "In another group, we showed people their income on a weekly basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 34490.0,
      "end_time": 38776.0,
      "text": "And what we found was that people who saw their income on a weekly basis"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 38800.0,
      "end_time": 41172.0,
      "text": "were able to budget better throughout the month."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 41196.0,
      "end_time": 42495.0,
      "text": "Now, it&#39;s important to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 42520.0,
      "end_time": 45297.0,
      "text": "that we didn&#39;t change how much money people were receiving,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 45321.0,
      "end_time": 48635.0,
      "text": "we just changed the environment in which they understood their income."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 48659.0,
      "end_time": 51104.0,
      "text": "And environmental cues like this have an impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 51128.0,
      "end_time": 54136.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m not going to share tricks with you that you already know."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 54160.0,
      "end_time": 56922.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not going to tell you how to open up a savings account"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 56946.0,
      "end_time": 58958.0,
      "text": "or how to start saving for your retirement."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 58982.0,
      "end_time": 61867.0,
      "text": "What I am going to share with you is how to bridge this gap"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 61891.0,
      "end_time": 63704.0,
      "text": "from your intentions to save"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 63728.0,
      "end_time": 65220.0,
      "text": "and your actions."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 65459.99999999999,
      "end_time": 66227.0,
      "text": "Are you ready?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 66251.0,
      "end_time": 67442.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s number one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 67466.0,
      "end_time": 69213.0,
      "text": "harness the power of pre-commitment."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 69237.0,
      "end_time": 72259.0,
      "text": "Fundamentally, we think about ourselves in two different ways:"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 72284.0,
      "end_time": 74745.0,
      "text": "our present self and our future self."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 74769.0,
      "end_time": 76420.0,
      "text": "In the future, we&#39;re perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 76444.0,
      "end_time": 78800.0,
      "text": "In the future, we&#39;re going to save for retirement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 78824.0,
      "end_time": 80119.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to lose weight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 80143.0,
      "end_time": 81936.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to call our parents more."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 81960.0,
      "end_time": 84850.0,
      "text": "But we oftentimes forget that our future self"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 84109.0,
      "end_time": 87149.0,
      "text": "is exactly the same person as our present self."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 87173.0,
      "end_time": 90752.0,
      "text": "We know that one of the best times to save is when you get your tax return."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 90776.0,
      "end_time": 92410.0,
      "text": "So we tried an A/B test."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 92434.0,
      "end_time": 95823.0,
      "text": "In the first group, we texted people in early February,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 95847.0,
      "end_time": 98298.0,
      "text": "hopefully before they even filed for their taxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 98323.0,
      "end_time": 99482.0,
      "text": "And we asked them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 99506.0,
      "end_time": 102843.0,
      "text": "\"If you get a tax refund, what percentage would you like to save?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 102867.0,
      "end_time": 104565.0,
      "text": "Now this is a really hard question."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 104589.0,
      "end_time": 108164.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t know if they would receive a tax refund or how much."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 108189.0,
      "end_time": 109881.0,
      "text": "But we asked the question anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 109906.0,
      "end_time": 114950.0,
      "text": "In the second group, we asked people right after they received their refund,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 114119.0,
      "end_time": 116950.0,
      "text": "\"What percentage would you like to save?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 116119.0,
      "end_time": 117413.0,
      "text": "Now, here&#39;s what happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 117437.0,
      "end_time": 121372.0,
      "text": "In that second condition, when people just received their tax refund,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 121396.0,
      "end_time": 124517.0,
      "text": "they wanted to save about 17 percent of their tax refund."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 124541.0,
      "end_time": 129560.0,
      "text": "But in the condition when we asked people before they even filed their taxes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 129800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133534.0,
      "text": "savings rates increased from 17 percent to 27 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 133558.0,
      "end_time": 134935.0,
      "text": "when we asked in February."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 134960.0,
      "end_time": 136130.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 136154.0,
      "end_time": 138370.0,
      "text": "Because you&#39;re committing for your future self,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 138394.0,
      "end_time": 141930.0,
      "text": "and of course your future self can save 27 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 141117.0,
      "end_time": 143720.0,
      "text": "These large changes in savings behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 143744.0,
      "end_time": 146903.0,
      "text": "came from the fact that we changed the decision-making environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 146927.0,
      "end_time": 149346.0,
      "text": "We want you to be able to harness that same power."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 149370.0,
      "end_time": 150630.0,
      "text": "So take a moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 150654.0,
      "end_time": 154690.0,
      "text": "and think about the ways in which you can sign up your future self"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 154930.0,
      "end_time": 157690.0,
      "text": "for something that you know today will be a little bit hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 157930.0,
      "end_time": 160751.0,
      "text": "Sign up for an app that lets you make savings decisions in advance."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 160776.0,
      "end_time": 163982.0,
      "text": "The trick is, you have to have that binding contract."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 164600.0,
      "end_time": 167608.0,
      "text": "Number two: use transition moments to your advantage."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 167632.0,
      "end_time": 169516.0,
      "text": "We did an experiment with a website"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 169540.0,
      "end_time": 172600.0,
      "text": "that helps older adults share their housing."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 172850.0,
      "end_time": 174370.0,
      "text": "We ran two ads on social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 174610.0,
      "end_time": 176903.0,
      "text": "targeted to the same population of 64-year-olds."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 176927.0,
      "end_time": 179968.0,
      "text": "In one group, we said, \"Hey, you&#39;re getting older."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 179992.0,
      "end_time": 181426.0,
      "text": "Are you ready for retirement?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 181450.0,
      "end_time": 182632.0,
      "text": "House sharing can help.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 182657.0,
      "end_time": 185473.0,
      "text": "In the second group, we got a little bit more specific"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 185497.0,
      "end_time": 187879.0,
      "text": "and said, \"You&#39;re 64 turning 65."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 187903.0,
      "end_time": 189328.0,
      "text": "Are you ready for retirement?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 189352.0,
      "end_time": 190680.0,
      "text": "House sharing can help.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 190704.0,
      "end_time": 192545.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;re doing in that second group"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 192569.0,
      "end_time": 195600.0,
      "text": "is highlighting that a transition is happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 195850.0,
      "end_time": 196236.0,
      "text": "All of a sudden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 199382.0,
      "text": "we saw click-through rates, and ultimately sign-up rates, increase"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 199406.0,
      "end_time": 200566.0,
      "text": "when we highlight that."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 200590.0,
      "end_time": 203307.0,
      "text": "In psychology, we call this the \"fresh start effect.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 203331.0,
      "end_time": 206506.0,
      "text": "Whether it&#39;s the start of a new year or even a new season,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 206530.0,
      "end_time": 208964.0,
      "text": "your motivation to act increases."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 208988.0,
      "end_time": 211537.0,
      "text": "So right now, put a meeting request on your calendar"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 211561.0,
      "end_time": 213442.0,
      "text": "for the day before your next birthday."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 213466.0,
      "end_time": 216558.0,
      "text": "Identify the one financial thing you most want to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 216863.0,
      "end_time": 218756.0,
      "text": "And commit yourself to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 218780.0,
      "end_time": 220497.0,
      "text": "The third and final trick:"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 220521.0,
      "end_time": 223712.0,
      "text": "get a handle on small, frequent purchases."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 223736.0,
      "end_time": 225768.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve run a few different studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 225792.0,
      "end_time": 230379.0,
      "text": "and found that the number one purchase people say they regret, after bank fees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 230403.0,
      "end_time": 231553.0,
      "text": "is eating out."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 231577.0,
      "end_time": 234355.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a frequent purchase we make almost every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 234379.0,
      "end_time": 236549.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s death by a thousand cuts."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 236574.0,
      "end_time": 238933.0,
      "text": "A coffee here, a burrito there ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 238957.0,
      "end_time": 241803.0,
      "text": "It adds up and decreases our ability to save."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 242513.0,
      "end_time": 244244.0,
      "text": "Back when I lived in New York City,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 244268.0,
      "end_time": 245649.0,
      "text": "I looked at my expenses"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 245673.0,
      "end_time": 249863.0,
      "text": "and saw that I spent over 2,000 dollars on ride-sharing apps."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 249887.0,
      "end_time": 251902.0,
      "text": "It was more than my New York City rent."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 251926.0,
      "end_time": 253727.0,
      "text": "I vowed to make a change."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 253752.0,
      "end_time": 256714.0,
      "text": "And the next month, I spent 2,000 dollars again --"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 256738.0,
      "end_time": 260553.0,
      "text": "no change, because the information alone didn&#39;t change my behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 260577.0,
      "end_time": 262276.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t change my environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 282618.0,
      "end_time": 283888.0,
      "text": "We aren&#39;t machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 283912.0,
      "end_time": 286364.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t carry around an abacus every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 286388.0,
      "end_time": 290730.0,
      "text": "adding up what we&#39;re spending, in comparison to what we wanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 290980.0,
      "end_time": 292352.0,
      "text": "But what our brains are very good at"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 292376.0,
      "end_time": 295527.0,
      "text": "is counting up the number of times we&#39;ve done something."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 295551.0,
      "end_time": 297336.0,
      "text": "So I gave myself a limit."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 297360.0,
      "end_time": 300918.0,
      "text": "I can only use ride-sharing apps three times a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 300942.0,
      "end_time": 303656.0,
      "text": "It forced me to ration my travels."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 303680.0,
      "end_time": 307338.0,
      "text": "I got a handle on my car-sharing expenses to the benefit of my husband,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 307362.0,
      "end_time": 309609.0,
      "text": "because of the environmental changes that I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 309633.0,
      "end_time": 312505.0,
      "text": "So get a handle on whatever that purchase is for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 312529.0,
      "end_time": 315502.0,
      "text": "and change your environment to make it harder to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 315895.0,
      "end_time": 317695.0,
      "text": "Those are my tips for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 317720.0,
      "end_time": 319855.0,
      "text": "But I want you to remember one thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 319879.0,
      "end_time": 323806.0,
      "text": "As human beings, we can be irrational when it comes to saving"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 323830.0,
      "end_time": 325704.0,
      "text": "and spending and budgeting."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 325728.0,
      "end_time": 327974.0,
      "text": "But luckily, we know this about ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 327998.0,
      "end_time": 331617.0,
      "text": "and we can predict how we&#39;ll act under certain environments."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 331641.0,
      "end_time": 333426.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s do that with saving."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 333450.0,
      "end_time": 336554.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s change our environment to help our future selves."
    }
  ]
}